b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">25</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$70.38 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">50</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$62.64 each</td></tr><tr class=\"border-b border-neutral-100\"><td class=\"py-2 pr-3 text-neutral-800 tabular-nums\">100</td><td class=\"py-2 tabular-nums\">$55.75 each</td></tr></tbody>\n</table>\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mt-5 mb-2\">Catalog highlights</h4><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-[13px] leading-snug\"><li>Mercury backpack. This bag is ready for anything and everything! Interior lining matches outer trim color. 13 W x 19 H x 6.5 D. Durable ripstop and 600 Denier polyester body fabrics. Colored 210 Denier polyester lining matches its exterior piping color. Soft plus shoulder straps for comfort. Ergonomically vented for airflow. Trendy colored accented highlights. 17 laptop pocket and tablet sleeve. Fits 17 laptop</li></ul>\n<div class=\"not-prose mt-5\">\n<h4 class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-neutral-700 mb-2\">Patch options (supplier)</h4>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600 mb-3\">Options and add-ons from the live Distributor Central product page for this SKU. Pricing may change; confirm on your quote.</p>\n<div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-lg border border-neutral-200 bg-neutral-50/30\">\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Product Style</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-ne